{"tid":746840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳港鐵荃灣線列車「衝燈」險追撞 系統急煞停","createTime":"2018-07-18T02:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T12:45:04.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3e1981d0af9c60d944c86c6fc9a9bfeb84e284","tid":746840,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A-%E8%A1%9D%E7%87%88-%E9%9A%AA%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%80%A5%E7%85%9E%E5%81%9C-002900144.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%2587%2588-%25E9%259A%25AA%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2592%259E-%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2580%25A5%25E7%2585%259E%25E5%2581%259C-002900144.html&d=S6G0BtnUd%2F2LN8rd4i%2FdH8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ca158297\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B3%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E7%B7%9A%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A-%E8%A1%9D%E7%87%88-%E9%9A%AA%E8%BF%BD%E6%92%9E-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%80%A5%E7%85%9E%E5%81%9C-002900144.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】港鐵荃灣線一列車，懷疑日前在荃灣站回廠時「衝紅燈」，在燈號指示不能前進時離開月台，險些撞到前方另一列車。本網正向港鐵了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事發於周一（7月16日）凌晨，當時肇事列車無載客，在荃灣站月台準備回廠，但當時月台信號燈顯示為紅燈。消息指，列車當時處於「手動模式」，懷疑有人繼續讓列車駛離月台，前方其實還有另一列車，幸好防護系統發現兩車距離異常接近，將「手動模式」緊急煞停。"},{"pid":"0f5aea8cc846fc8ee021002cc3b695c2591f85dd","tid":746840,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"b1750319c6ce7abebaeddb834b9da93d4ee86d8d","tid":746840,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"「齋講」消息 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4607be59007e356e178af5fa4058150116143fc","tid":746840,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"cit